One time for a PC

1. Create heroku account
2. verify email
3. install heroku cli
4. heroku login

One time for each project

1. heroku create 
2. make sure to update git add & push
3. git push heroku main
4. Go to Heroku dashboard > Current project > Settings > Reveal Config
5. Copy Paste config from env
6. Make sure you have whiteListed all ip address to access mongodb

Update server

1. Make changes
2. Make sure to update git add & push
3. git push heroku main